    <!-- Vector icon library (24x24 viewbox path data, Material Design Icons geometry). Referenced by
         custom controls and views via {StaticResource Icon...}. Keeping every glyph here means icons
         recolour with the theme (they are painted with theme brushes at the usage site) and stay
         consistent across the app. Render them inside a 24x24 Canvas/Viewbox so asymmetric glyphs stay
         centred — IconButton and the Path.icon style do this for you. -->

